    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> For other OS use a different legend of single letters.\"\n\nAt some poiint we want shortcut in menu. Obviously, `Ctrl-Alt-Shift-M` is too long for menu, but if we asssume C==Ctrl, Alt ==M == Meta , Shift == S, we could write it `CMS-M` (shift could be keept as arrow), but C==Ctrl, and M==Meta (S sometime == Super == windows key on linux) are common. \n"
